Q.
Look at the following code (with line numbers for clarity) and say where each of the following variables is visible:
i, j, newSize, size.

 class UnitMatrix {
   int size;

   void setSize(int newSize) {
     this.size = newSize;
   }

   void print() {
     for (int i = 0; i < size; i++) {
       for (int j = 0; j < size; j++) {
         if (i == j) {
           println("1 ");
         } else {
           println("0 ");
         }
       }
       println ""
     }
   }
 }

say where each of the following variables is visible:

A.
i = lines 09-18
j = lines 10-16
newSize = lines 4-6
size = 0-19
